org.researchstack.skin

Class TaskProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.researchstack.skin.TaskProvider

  • public abstract class TaskProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    TaskProvider is used as a way for the Framework to get Tasks needed throughout the onboarding process. This allows you to implement your own Tasks if needed.
